|---|---|---|
| No security headers | High | Add `helmet` |
| No rate limiting | High | Add `express-rate-limit` |
| No global error handler | High | Add `app.use((err, req, res, next) => {...})` |
| No 404 handler | Medium | Add catch-all route |
| Hardcoded data/port | Medium | Use env vars & DB |
| No CORS policy | Medium | Add `cors` middleware |
| No body parsing limits | Medium | Add `express.json({ limit })` |
