|---|-------|----------|-----------|
| 1 | No security headers | ­¤ö┤ High | Add `helmet` |
| 2 | No rate limiting | ­¤ö┤ High | Add `express-rate-limit` |
| 3 | No global error handler | ­¤¤Ā Medium | Add error middleware |
| 4 | No input validation | ­¤¤Ā Medium | Use `zod` / `joi` |
| 5 | No body size limit | ­¤¤Ā Medium | Set `express.json({ limit })` |
| 6 | Hardcoded port | ­¤¤Ī Low | Use `process.env.PORT` |
| 7 | No graceful shutdown | ­¤¤Ī Low | Handle `SIGTERM` |

